name: Samantha Landrum "Hometown" Recipe Book/CD Single
description: Simply put, Samantha's "Hometown" Recipe Book/CD Single is a must-have collector's item! Packed with Landrum Family recipes, the book features everything from recipes for Muffins and Dumplings to Cheeseburger Pie to Cream Cheese Cookies, and more! In addition, the Recipe Book contains a limited edition "Hometown" CD single, and each recipe book is autographed by Samantha herself! A portion of the proceeds from the sale of the "Hometown" Recipe Book benefits The Women And Cancer Fund NOTE: Price includes shipping and handling - Limited time offer!

name: Samantha Landrum Elegance Bangle Set
description: Samantha Landrum proudly introduces Elegance by Bellissima Jewelers, a bangle set that symbolizes Samantha's unending pursuit of her dream. Beautiful set of three bangles are as classic and simple as Samantha's country roots. They complement any outfit and fit your every mood, from jeans to evening, work to recreation.
